<article class="page">
  <div class="page__container">
    <h1 class="page__title">Downloads</h1>

    <p>Aqui é possível baixar os mapas e mosaicos de imagens Landsat das coleções 1 e 2 do MapBiomas. Também são fornecidos acessos a plataforma de downloads dos mapas de referencia utilizados pelo MapBiomas.</p>
    <div class="downloads">
      <div class="downloads__mapbiomas_collection">
        <div class="downloads__icon">
          <%= link_to (image_tag "icon-collection.png"), page_path('database/mapbiomas_collection') %>
        </div>
        <strong><%= link_to 'Mapas das coleções', page_path('database/mapbiomas_collection') %></strong>
      </div>

      <div class="downloads__reference_maps">
        <div class="downloads__icon">
          <%= link_to (image_tag "icon-reference-pb.png"), page_path('database/reference_maps') %>
        </div>
        <strong><%= link_to 'Mapas de referência', page_path('database/reference_maps') %></strong>
      </div>

      <div class="downloads__landsat_mosaics">
        <div class="downloads__icon">
          <%= link_to (image_tag "icon-landsat.png"), page_path('database/landsat_mosaics') %>
        </div>
        <strong><%= link_to 'Mosaicos Landsat', page_path('database/landsat_mosaics') %></strong>
      </div>

      <div class="downloads__cod_legend">
        <div class="downloads__icon">
          <%= link_to (image_tag "icon-cod_legend.png"), "https://s3.amazonaws.com/mapbiomas-ecostage/legenda_mapbiomas.pdf", target: "_blank" %>
        </div>
        <strong><%= link_to 'Código da legenda', "https://s3.amazonaws.com/mapbiomas-ecostage/legenda_mapbiomas.pdf", target: "_blank" %></strong>
      </div>

      <div class="downloads__mapbiomas_collection">
        <div class="downloads__icon">
          <%= image_tag "icon-mural.png" %>
        </div>
        <strong>Mapa Mural (<%= link_to '.TIFF', "https://www.lapig.iesa.ufg.br/drive/index.php/s/6mdzr5E4wUnG2M5", target: "_blank" %>/<%= link_to '.PDF', "https://s3.amazonaws.com/mapbiomas-ecostage/Base+de+dados/Mapa+Mural/Mapa_Mapbiomas_500_2015_v3.pdf", target: "_blank" %>)
        </strong>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>
